{"tid":666664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"模特老闆辣到噴鼻血　他追不到偷私味洩慾","createTime":"2018-05-16T05:25:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T06:23:47.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a49d9115073aaadfbec45e051137e4ced3431fa0","tid":666664,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:25:56.000Z","msg":"台南市邱姓男子是新娘秘書載客司機，對身材火辣的許姓女老闆日久生情，多次向對方表白遭拒，他竟潛入工作室偷抹女老闆香水，甚至到自助洗衣店偷走10多件內衣褲後消失。女老闆發現後直呼噁心，日前向台南市第五警分局報案，警方偵辦中。<br />\n <br />\n37歲許姓女子是新娘秘書工作室負責人，她曾是外拍模特兒，擁有好身材。半年前她剛結束一段7年感情，目前全心投入工作，租下一間小套房，當作化妝、攝影的工作室。由於她與婚禮攝影配合，常要到拍攝點幫忙化妝，今年初經朋友介紹，聘請邱姓男子（34歲）當司機。<br />\n <br />\n許女說，邱男主要工作是負責載送客人，有空在幫忙處理工作室瑣事，她跟邱男工作3個多月，對方數度向她告白，但都遭到拒絕。由於工作室共用，邱男竟然到工作室偷擦她的香水、化妝品，載她時還跟她說「味道很香」、「身上有你的味道」，讓她覺得很不舒服。<br />\n <br />\n許女說，邱男偶爾摸走工作室內的預備金，被發現時，又向她求情說，因為手頭緊，先借給邱男，爾後從薪水裡扣。許女認為，既然是工作夥伴，暫時先不要撕破臉，不料邱男直接偷走1萬多元的備用金，還到洗衣店偷走她的內褲。<br />\n <br />\n許女表示，上周打電話要邱男載她去洗衣店拿回衣物，但對方手機關機，她到洗衣店後發現，只剩下毛巾，10多件內衣褲全都不翼而飛。警方調閱監視器才發現是邱男偷的，就連工作室的預備金也被偷。<br />\n <br />\n台南市第五警分局開元派出所長莊文輝說，警方已受理報案，目前正設法聯繫邱男到案說明。（辛啟松／台南報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180516/640_d982cd6456d60e8342610ea9644c0641.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180516%2F640_d982cd6456d60e8342610ea9644c0641.jpg&h=a3dee487&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許姓新娘秘書擁有好身材。翻攝畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180516/640_a58bebca94194060eb151f839ed206e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180516%2F640_a58bebca94194060eb151f839ed206e9.jpg&h=c3bdcad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n許姓新娘秘書曾是外拍模特兒，擁有好身材。翻攝畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180516/640_79e4dfeeed981f17359fe13cd2790bfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180516%2F640_79e4dfeeed981f17359fe13cd2790bfe.jpg&h=9605c7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n秋姓男子涉嫌偷走許姓婚秘的內衣褲。翻攝畫面<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180516/1354841/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180516%2F1354841%2F&d=UFwGXX8V4%2F2YAQ8xCHZgtDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a7328d9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180516%2F1354841%2F&h=24ca8f7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180516/1354841/</a>"},{"pid":"ce0941c6cf5763407a6c42b4b434ed0283993d7d","tid":666664,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"你屌埋我果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2838b4dcb2eb871cb5053cfa33b7434a18dd74f","tid":666664,"uid":82940,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:27:22.000Z","msg":"台灣+1分"},{"pid":"68872237f7a68ea1ac427d6efd42b2ceeb95b0c7","tid":666664,"uid":63588,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:49:32.000Z","msg":"我屌埋你嗰份"},{"pid":"967b05794ba5372772ad562e00a9a16d52890a91","tid":666664,"uid":71342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ce0941c6cf5763407a6c42b4b434ed0283993d7d","tid":666664,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":16,"score":-16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"你屌埋我果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T05:54:38.000Z","msg":"睇完片，似大媽格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32179f78b622267ab79a510b62441237addeeb3b","tid":666664,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:00:10.000Z","msg":"唐姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94e75ee8b8c91c4632a6dfa72011cba4f47b1b3","tid":666664,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:02:26.000Z","msg":"鳴呀"},